*美國駐日陸軍基地軍樂隊（{{lang|en|U.S. Army Garrison, Japan, Band}}）<ref>[http://www.usarj.army.mil/organization/296band/ U.S. Army Japan Band :: Home] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130730045849/http://www.usarj.army.mil/organization/296band/ |date=2013-07-30 }}</ref>
